54881,"uid":247855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T01:58:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/REbJsO7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FREbJsO7.gif&h=397803cd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4934dc945d1e5b1d0e6ba703cfd16a92a3c2eaaa","tid":1654881,"uid":224885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T02:44:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1811f217ade80fde1c83ee25ab94e47c1da2f7e3","tid":1654881,"uid":64380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T02:47:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbb03c3661701bcbaff3410416f454f71ef0d1a2","tid":1654881,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T03:26:30.000Z","msg":"So sweet....My friend Sarah is an Aries whereas her boyfriend is a Scorpio. She honours her parents. She's thankful for what her parents have done for her. Her brother is also a good son whereas her sister needs to be a better daughter. In the east teachers and parents stress the importance of filial piety which means chinese parental respect. They teach that you should honour your parents and take care of them. Recently her cousin stope her watchstrap. It was a matter of honour to tell her about it. My brother was honour bound to tell her too. Her dad is a man of honour and high integrity. Both of us are kickboxing fans. In January Fred will be fighting chris for the honour of his country. Winning the championship is a matter of personal honour, family honour and national honour. Last month Fred's church held a banquet in honour of him. Sarah asked whether I could do her the honour of accompanying her to the banquet which I did. It was signal honour to meet Fred. Fred said humbly &quot;it's a great honour to have you here Sarah&quot; We asked him if he would do us the honour of becoming our kickboxing coach. He said &quot;we'll see&quot; A couple of waiters did the honours and greeted the guests at the door. After we sat down Fred asked the waitress &quot;will you do the honours and cut us a piece of chicken?&quot; Fred said to us &quot;I would be honoured if you could come and see my fight in January&quot; We gave him an affirmative response. Last year the chairman of the kickboxing organisation said &quot;I would be honoured if you attended the hall of fame event&quot; which he did. He was honoured for his performance in his last fight. Besides winning the championship he was honoured with an award for excellence in grappling. By the way many people bought front row tickets for the next kickboxing event at half price or less due to a computer error but the organisation stated they would honour these tickets nevertheless which could cost a million dollars in lost earnings. Sarah's great grandfather accepted a commission as a sergeant major in the army. He was buried with full military honours."},{"pid":"7e31d06bf7d7acb9942c4d220c0895c3799c2ac0","tid":1654881,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0fb7030a3c517ec7425c4f1b16ea655845efd419","tid":1654881,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fac1c197696661070eda19a98674caa3a1fb69eb","tid":1654881,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"182d62b8518574e0424b42e1f83b9303a377d3a5","tid":1654881,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T20:24:57.000Z","msg":"冬天真係好舒服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />食雪糕"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T20:26:35.000Z","msg":"睇完個妹妹ig片之後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T20:42:23.000Z","msg":"link...?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"